Ok so this one requires a bit of an explanation since I don’t talk much of how it all started with Mira and warp, I will say this song challenge is really helping me get more involved in other parts of my story! So a big part of the story is a redemption arch for Warp, it’s a decision he makes on his own, there is a whole back story of why, but I’ll get to that later. anyway this takes place after warp has left zurg (or well got ratted out, when he was kinda under cover for buzz…again lost story) 

This song I feel captures this point in time for warp, he’s getting his karma in a sense, but also he’s trying to fix some of his wrongs, teaming up with buzz to try and stop zurg from something that could actually put the entire galaxy in danger (and not just zurg being the danger…) However now he is considered a traitor on both sides and the only person who has his back is buzz (like Mira is telling buzz this is a bad idea trusting warp, of course her view changes later after she’s been stuck with warp on the mission lol ) also warp’s arm from zurg was an experiment that didn’t go well….kinda messed him up 😅which is why he is in the hospital 

And yes my head cannon is buzz and warp grew up together, a good reason why buzz knows warp is not as evil as he puts outand it is the first one to welcome him back! 

(Also if none of this makes any sense, I am half alseep and will edit in the morning, GOOD NIGHT!)
